	OnWhoGuardian
	{
		articleopencount++
		
		"\0\s[0]\t\*\b2Oh, you want to know more about little old me? \s[1]I'm flattered.\n \w3\s[0]...I'm afraid there isn't much for me to tell you, however. I am but an ordinary Pip, born in \_a[OnAnianaprefecture]Ani'ana Prefecture\_a...\w9 when, you ask? Oh...\s[1]\w9 long ago. \s[0]Most definitely before anyone you know, ha. \s[1]My years are plenty, and they have woven themselves into me quite snugly... I may appear young to the untrained eye, but I have weathered quite the storm, as they say.\n\n \s[0]Anyways, ahem... long ago, I was chosen as the \_a[OnWhatGuardians]Shrine Guardian\_a of Kosanu. With how highly I speak of the honor, you'd think it would be some divine blessing, granted unto me by the Firsts themselves... \s[3]but, ehm, I simply performed more efficiently in the ceremonial training than my peers, as is the case with the other Guardians, haha.\n \s[0]Even if I hadn't been chosen, I think I still would have "
		--
			if locslot == "shrine"
			{
				"dedicated myself to this place"
			}
			else
			{
				"dedicated my life to the shrine"
			}
		--
		". All I have ever wanted is to immerse myself in history...\w2\s[1] and what better way to do so than to take care of a temple that has been here for over a thousand years?\n\n\w9\w6\s[0]Ah, right. I suppose there are other things I failed to mention about myself... er, I translate classic Kosani literature into Common. I also write my own, though it is more often nonfiction; accounts of history, rewritten with a more honeyed tongue... \s[1]to appease the poet in my heart, while satiating my brain's hunger for knowledge.\n\n \s[0]\w3...Let's see, what else...\w4 \s[1]ah, how could I forget?\n \w3\s[0]As you surely have gathered, I am a traveller. I have settled down since my younger days, but I have been all across the landmass, as well as beyond it. I have visited cities large and small, islands near and far... and I have seen incredible things on my journeys.\n \w6\s[1]...The thing I love most is sharing these experiences with any soul that wants to hear them.\n\w9It was kind of you to ask about me, %(oomf). I hope this answer suffices."
		--
		"\n\n\n\![*]\q[Back to dictionary,OnBACK]\n\![*]\q[Thank you,Cancel]\n"
		
		if Flag("who article read") == 0; MiscFlags ,= "who article read"
	}

